OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine throughout, with some
OL,6,Fsunshine, although this may turn
OL,7,Frather rather hazy at times under high
OL,8,Fcloud. Becoming widely hot, although a
OL,9,Flittle less so in eastern coastal
OL,10,Fdistricts. Winds staying light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FEvening sunny periods will
OL,13,Flead into a dry night, staying very
OL,14,Fwarm for many, especially in larger
OL,15,Fcities. Feeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
